				<h4>Parameters</h4>
				<pre>?date={string:date}</pre>
				<h4>Description</h4>
				<p>Queries with this parameter will return the games played or to be played on the date given. When using this parameter, make sure to convert your date to YYYYMMDD format.</p>
				<p><b>NOTE</b>: This parameter will only return data for the current season. If you want data from previous seasons, see the <a href="#season">seasons</a> parameter.</p>

